# RQ-53-10-01-155: Paint Scheme Requirements

## Requirement Statement
Nose cone paint shall meet durability and weight requirements without affecting radar performance.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Paint weight < 2 kg total
- No metallic paint on radome (RF interference)
- Erosion-resistant topcoat
- Service life 5 years between repaints

## Compliance Status
Paint specification released
